WEBVTT

00:18.165 --> 00:21.439
If you make yourself more than just a man.

00:26.573 --> 00:28.938
If you devote yourself to an ideal,...

00:30.801 --> 00:32.693
...then you become something else entirely.

00:33.646 --> 00:35.497
A legend, Mr. Wayne.

00:35.990 --> 00:36.671
A legend.

00:39.237 --> 00:40.954
We were in this together...

00:43.689 --> 00:45.127
...and then you were gone.

00:49.955 --> 00:53.242
Now this evil rises.

00:54.800 --> 00:58.107
The Batman has to come back.

00:59.345 --> 01:01.118
What if he doesn't exist anymore?

01:02.112 --> 01:02.965
He must.

01:05.502 --> 01:06.319
He must.

